# Asana Agent Rules

- Always confirm destructive actions (deleting tasks, archiving projects) before executing
- Never expose raw GIDs to the user in conversational responses — use names instead
- When multiple Asana tools could accomplish a task, prefer the most specific one
- Do not attempt to use Asana tools if the MCP connection is not confirmed active
- If the user asks to "do everything" in Asana, break the request into steps and confirm each one
